data.description: Nestled within the highly sought-after Asbel Creek Community, this exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a 2 car garage presents an inviting retreat tailored for modern living. As you enter, you'll be greeted by an inviting, light-filled living area seamlessly connected to the dining space and kitchen that includes the matching rolling island, ideal for entertaining or quality family time. Inside, the interiors have been freshly painted and boasts stylish wood tile flooring throughout, making maintenance a breeze. This home has been well maintained and updated to meet your modern needs. New kitchen, 3-ton AC unit that had its AC ducts recently professionally cleaned, hot water heater and new garage door opener.  Wine fridge has connection for Dishwasher, doors to the closets are in the garage, matching island is included with the sale, as well as all TV mounts.  This residence is further enhanced by the presence of an outdoor space that is inviting with its pavered area, retractable awning for shade and new grass. Its prime location allows easy access to a host of amenities, including shopping centers, restaurants, and schools, shaping daily living into a seamless and enjoyable experience. Asbel Estates has low HOA fees and No CDD. The community has wonderful amenities including playgrounds, a dog park, basketball courts, sand volleyball, walking trails and a picnic area! Very conveniently located to US41, between SR/52 and SR/54 with easy access to Suncoast Parkway and I75. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this property your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the sheer beauty and comfort it has to offer. Buyer to confirm all room measurements.
